description: Gets information about the specified report generator.

parameters.name: LicenseManagerReportGeneratorArn
parameters.description: Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the report generator.

nested_items.name: ReportGenerator
nested_items.description: A report generator that creates periodic reports about your license configurations.

nested_items.name: ReportGeneratorName
nested_items.description: Name of the report generator.

nested_items.name: ReportType
nested_items.description: Type of reports that are generated.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: ReportContext
nested_items.description: License configuration type for this generator.

nested_items.name: licenseConfigurationArns
nested_items.description: Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the license configuration that this generator reports on.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: ReportFrequency
nested_items.description: Details about how frequently reports are generated.

nested_items.name: value
nested_items.description: Number of times within the frequency period that a report is generated. The only supported value is 1.

nested_items.name: period
nested_items.description: Time period between each report. The period can be daily, weekly, or monthly.

nested_items.name: LicenseManagerReportGeneratorArn
nested_items.description: Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the report generator.

nested_items.name: LastRunStatus
nested_items.description: Status of the last report generation attempt.

nested_items.name: LastRunFailureReason
nested_items.description: Failure message for the last report generation attempt.

nested_items.name: LastReportGenerationTime
nested_items.description: Time the last report was generated at.

nested_items.name: ReportCreatorAccount
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID used to create the report generator.

nested_items.name: Description
nested_items.description: Description of the report generator.

nested_items.name: S3Location
nested_items.description: Details of the S3 bucket that report generator reports are published to.

nested_items.name: bucket
nested_items.description: Name of the S3 bucket reports are published to.

nested_items.name: keyPrefix
nested_items.description: Prefix of the S3 bucket reports are published to.

nested_items.description: Time the report was created.
